headline: Cboe Commemorates 40 Years of Options Education with The Options Institute
summary: Cboe Global Markets, Inc. (Cboe: CBOE), the world's leading derivatives and securities exchange network, this year celebrates the 40th anniversary of The Options Institute, the company's educational division. To mark this milestone, Cboe is launching a year-long commemoration – beginning during National Financial Literacy Month – to honor The Options Institute's decades-long impact on options education and financial literacy worldwide, while looking ahead to its continued evolution in the years
